1
00:00:18,490 --> 00:00:23,460
<i>[The World I Love - Liu Yuning]</i>

2
00:00:23,460 --> 00:00:27,460
♫ <i>Dark night, wet moon, and cold blood</i> ♫

3
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,400
♫ <i>Made the naked pupils in my eyes afraid of the light</i> ♫

4
00:00:31,400 --> 00:00:34,640
♫ <i>Is it bright and warm?</i> ♫

5
00:00:34,640 --> 00:00:39,100
♫ <i>I can only guess based on intuition</i> ♫

6
00:00:39,100 --> 00:00:47,220
♫ <i>Ah, love pouring over the world like jade, granting me good luck</i> ♫

7
00:00:47,220 --> 00:00:55,740
♫ <i>Ah, the thread of love is coiled strongly around me</i> ♫

8
00:00:55,740 --> 00:01:03,140
♫ <i>I do not fear how people treat me in this world</i> ♫

9
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:07,180
♫ <i>Breaking through, struggling to escape</i> ♫

10
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,600
♫ <i>How to differentiate between good and bad</i> ♫

11
00:01:11,600 --> 00:01:19,240
♫ <i> There are times when I'm fragile, to heal wounds with a kiss of love</i> ♫

12
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:23,260
♫ <i>My existence</i> ♫

13
00:01:23,260 --> 00:01:31,300
♫ <i>Thorns won't break my wings</i> ♫

14
00:01:31,300 --> 00:01:36,160
<i>[Till The End of The Moon]</i>

15
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:39,430
<i>[Episode 31]</i>

16
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:43,140
<i>[The Hengyang Sect]</i>
Jiumin, this is the Hengyang Sect.

17
00:01:43,140 --> 00:01:44,583
Let's go.

18
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:50,430
The Immortal Sect Competition will be held here in a few days.

19
00:01:50,430 --> 00:01:53,030
I'll bring you to widen your horizon first.

20
00:01:54,710 --> 00:01:57,390
It's really magnificent, huh?

21
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:03,420
Follow me to go and meet Sect Leader Qu.

22
00:02:07,380 --> 00:02:09,380
Allow me to introduce him.

23
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:12,810
This is my new disciple, Cang Jiumin.

24
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:17,710
<i>It's him. He was just like Master.</i>

25
00:02:17,710 --> 00:02:20,760
<i>They were both killed by me as the Devil Lord.</i>

26
00:02:24,580 --> 00:02:27,730
I'm Jiumin. Nice to meet you, Sect Leader Qu Xuanzi.

27
00:02:27,730 --> 00:02:29,173
Have a seat.

28
00:02:33,630 --> 00:02:35,363
Not bad.

29
00:02:35,363 --> 00:02:38,610
Zhaoyou, you finally took in a normal-looking disciple.

30
00:02:38,610 --> 00:02:42,810
This is your biggest progress in the last century or so.

31
00:02:42,810 --> 00:02:46,710
What are you saying? You do not know how to give compliments.

32
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:52,363
Jiumin, you came at a bad time.

33
00:02:52,363 --> 00:02:55,750
My daughter, Li Susu, just left.

34
00:02:55,750 --> 00:03:00,380
I'll call her back now. I'll let you two meet.

35
00:03:00,380 --> 00:03:05,260
Thanks, Sect Leader Qu. But since I entered the Xiaoyao Sect, I've decided to focus on cultivation.

36
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:06,590
Nothing else interests me.

37
00:03:06,590 --> 00:03:11,790
If we're fated to meet, I'll meet Miss Susu next time.

38
00:03:12,470 --> 00:03:17,070
Today, I'm here to consult you about something.

39
00:03:17,070 --> 00:03:22,600
Sure, go ahead and ask. I'll see what I can do.

40
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:25,630
500 years ago, I used to live in Sheng Kingdom.

41
00:03:25,630 --> 00:03:31,060
I had a friend who resembled your disciple, Gongye Jiwu.

42
00:03:31,060 --> 00:03:34,260
I wonder if there's something mystic about it.

43
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:51,360
<i>Jiwu has no parents. He's not even a "normal" human.</i>

44
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:55,170
<i>He was originally Xiao Lin, the nephew of Immortal Buxu from the Xiaoyao Sect.</i>

45
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:58,800
<i>An unknown sudden incident took his life.</i>

46
00:04:00,140 --> 00:04:02,540
<i>Back then, Immortal Buxu came to the Hengyang Sect</i>

47
00:04:02,540 --> 00:04:05,890
<i>and borrowed an immortal artifact called the Crystal Bowl.</i>

48
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:13,330
<i>It's said to be made by the ancient God of War.</i>

49
00:04:13,330 --> 00:04:18,530
<i>Although it was slightly broken, it could still help to nurture souls.</i>

50
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:25,470
<i>He put Xiao Lin's soul in it</i>

51
00:04:25,470 --> 00:04:29,310
<i>and sank it into a divine energy-rich spot in Heaven Lake for nourishment.</i>

52
00:04:31,310 --> 00:04:37,060
<i>Since then, the Crystal Bowl gradually thawed several centuries later.</i>

53
00:04:37,060 --> 00:04:41,120
<i>With the nourishment of divine power, a baby was born.</i>

54
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:45,060
<i>I named the child Gongye Jiwu.</i>

55
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:56,770
I think you've guessed...

56
00:04:58,730 --> 00:05:00,360
who he really is.

57
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,390
Yes.

58
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:07,030
He's such a special person. Don't you want to talk me out of keeping him in my sect?

59
00:05:07,030 --> 00:05:09,750
Martial Granduncle Buxu doesn't make mistakes.

60
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,750
I also think Jiumin is a good kid.

61
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:19,400
If there's a good chance to enlighten him, he might achieve something great.

62
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,500
I trust your vision.

63
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:24,630
Not bad. Now you know how to compliment me, huh?

64
00:05:24,630 --> 00:05:27,320
I was complimenting your disciple.

65
00:06:26,020 --> 00:06:27,800
<i>I did it.</i>

66
00:06:28,460 --> 00:06:33,190
Pang Yizhi, now I know how you rebuilt Xiao Lin's body.

67
00:06:33,190 --> 00:06:37,090
The Heaven Lake of the Hengyang Sect is beautiful.

68
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:46,470
Sect Leader Qu of the Hengyang Sect has told me everything.

69
00:06:46,470 --> 00:06:50,200
You once asked me for a bottle of my heart blood.

70
00:06:50,200 --> 00:06:53,780
It must be one of the conditions to rebuild him.

71
00:06:53,780 --> 00:06:59,690
As for the rest, even if you don't tell me, I'll find out by myself one by one.

72
00:07:00,730 --> 00:07:02,800
To rebuild the body of a deceased person,

73
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:06,350
you'll need the blood of his enemy, the tears of his lover, and the hair and flesh of the deceased himself.

74
00:07:06,350 --> 00:07:12,360
Finally, you'll need to activate the Soul-Gathering Array where divine energy is most abundant.

75
00:07:14,070 --> 00:07:19,570
The tears of Ye Xiwu's lover and the blood of her enemy. I have them both.

76
00:07:19,570 --> 00:07:22,060
These are not difficult to acquire.

77
00:07:22,060 --> 00:07:25,930
As for her hair and flesh…

78
00:07:32,460 --> 00:07:37,110
<i>This eye was hers in the first place.</i>

79
00:07:37,110 --> 00:07:42,223
At worst, I'll gouge it out and return it to her.

80
00:07:43,220 --> 00:07:45,620
I'll still need the magic array.

81
00:07:45,620 --> 00:07:48,750
Where can I learn the Soul-gathering Array?

82
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:55,170
You can't bring back the dead. Practicing this spell is against nature's way.

83
00:07:55,170 --> 00:07:58,580
You're doing it to satisfy your own obsession.

84
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:05,040
You're trying to stop me?

85
00:08:05,040 --> 00:08:08,210
Is this why you've been keeping Gongye Jiwu safe?

86
00:08:08,210 --> 00:08:13,500
Because you felt guilty toward him. But you did it despite knowing this.

87
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:17,020
You simply miss her.

88
00:08:17,020 --> 00:08:21,950
But it's really unnecessary to cast this spell to rebuild her.

89
00:08:21,950 --> 00:08:24,200
What do you mean by unnecessary?

90
00:08:26,170 --> 00:08:29,840
I've lived five hundred years just to find her.

91
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:45,940
Pang Yizhi, you can't stop me.

92
00:08:59,250 --> 00:09:04,330
Brother Gongye, you look unsettled and troubled.

93
00:09:04,330 --> 00:09:07,740
Did something happen?

94
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:12,130
This was supposed to be a good thing.

95
00:09:12,130 --> 00:09:14,400
My junior sect sister, Li Susu,

96
00:09:14,400 --> 00:09:16,850
safely got out of her meditation retreat a few days ago.

97
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:23,600
So, she is the cause of your concerns?

98
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:30,340
After she came back, she seemed to have experienced something drastic and became completely different.

99
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:34,730
She has a pure-spirit body. Master was extremely protective of her.

100
00:09:34,730 --> 00:09:39,940
I grew up with her, but she had never been in love or understood it.

101
00:09:39,940 --> 00:09:43,250
Now, she seems like a different person after going through her tribulation.

102
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:45,900
I don't know how to approach her.

103
00:09:51,220 --> 00:09:55,053
Brother Gongye, don't be so pessimistic.

104
00:09:55,053 --> 00:09:58,170
She didn't understand love in the past,

105
00:09:58,170 --> 00:10:00,910
so she couldn't really respond to your feelings.

106
00:10:00,910 --> 00:10:03,610
Now, she's all grown up.

107
00:10:03,610 --> 00:10:06,390
Even if it means you have to start anew,

108
00:10:06,390 --> 00:10:10,180
isn't it a chance for you to win her heart?

109
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:17,030
To be honest with you, actually, I…

110
00:10:17,620 --> 00:10:20,720
I was born 500 years ago.

111
00:10:22,290 --> 00:10:24,323
500 years ago?

112
00:10:24,323 --> 00:10:26,103
Yes.

113
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:29,780
I had no emotions or love back then.

114
00:10:30,910 --> 00:10:35,010
I couldn't even feel ordinary happiness or sadness

115
00:10:35,010 --> 00:10:37,030
until someone showed up.

116
00:10:37,030 --> 00:10:41,000
This person taught me what love,

117
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,750
happiness, and sadness was.

118
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:46,170
And then?

119
00:10:46,170 --> 00:10:49,910
Then, I could finally feel her feelings for me.

120
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:51,530
But I couldn't make her stay.

121
00:10:51,530 --> 00:10:53,930
I've been searching for her for 500 years.

122
00:10:56,340 --> 00:11:00,730
If she can make you think of her and miss her until now,

123
00:11:00,730 --> 00:11:03,160
she must be your true love.

124
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:05,840
You mentioned it so lightly,

125
00:11:06,940 --> 00:11:12,040
but I assume it must be a sad story that agonizes you.

126
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:16,610
Love often results in sorrow. I guess I should take my time.

127
00:11:16,610 --> 00:11:21,300
I've waited ten years after all. To be frank with you,

128
00:11:21,300 --> 00:11:24,240
I feel particularly close to you.

129
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:27,210
I don't need to hide anything in front of you.

130
00:11:27,210 --> 00:11:30,230
I can say whatever I want straightforwardly.

131
00:11:33,940 --> 00:11:38,080
Although we've only met not long ago, you feel like an old friend.

132
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:42,700
I keep feeling that we've been close friends for many years.

133
00:11:43,890 --> 00:11:49,610
To me, you're already my old friend.

134
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:53,990
I used to have a friend whom I was indebted to.

135
00:11:53,990 --> 00:11:57,000
He looked just like you.

136
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,920
I've admired him and imitated him...

137
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:07,993
since young. I wanted to live like him.

138
00:12:09,860 --> 00:12:15,693
Now, I've joined the immortal sect to learn immortal arts...

139
00:12:16,740 --> 00:12:19,340
and make friends like you.

140
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:23,730
Maybe I have

141
00:12:23,730 --> 00:12:26,840
a chance to live like him now.

142
00:12:27,410 --> 00:12:29,870
I cherish this a lot.

143
00:12:32,380 --> 00:12:36,650
I think it's also my pleasure to befriend you, Junior Brother Jiumin.

144
00:12:45,670 --> 00:12:49,140
You have a strong heart and an intelligent mind.

145
00:12:49,140 --> 00:12:52,220
I cherish the days of cultivating together with you in the Xiaoyao Sect.

146
00:12:52,220 --> 00:12:56,510
Although I don't know what you've been through, it doesn't matter.

147
00:12:56,510 --> 00:13:00,600
No matter what happened in the past, you will always be my friend.

148
00:13:01,650 --> 00:13:03,583
Friend?

149
00:13:05,570 --> 00:13:11,830
By the way, Junior Brother Jiumin, I think you haven't told me why you came

150
00:13:11,830 --> 00:13:15,220
to seek me out today.

151
00:13:18,000 --> 00:13:23,640
I heard that your sect has a spell called the Soul-Gathering Array.

152
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:27,250
Have you heard of it before?

153
00:13:32,040 --> 00:13:34,500
<i>[Scripture Hall]</i>

154
00:14:00,020 --> 00:14:01,120
<i>[Guide to Devils]</i>

155
00:14:01,120 --> 00:14:02,360
<i>Guide to Devils?</i>

156
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:07,450
<i>Speaking of which, I am still unaware of the Devil Lord's tale yet.</i>

157
00:14:07,450 --> 00:14:08,630
<i>[Sky-Slashing Sword]</i>

158
00:14:08,630 --> 00:14:11,900
<i>The Sky-Slashing Sword is the Devil Lord's hand.</i>

159
00:14:11,900 --> 00:14:14,911
<i> [Bone-Refining Seal]</i>
<i>The Bone-Refining Seal is his heart.</i>

160
00:14:14,911 --> 00:14:15,810
<i>[God-Slaying Crossbow]</i>

161
00:14:15,810 --> 00:14:18,020
<i>It's that crossbow.</i>

162
00:14:19,490 --> 00:14:22,090
So that's the God-Slaying Crossbow.

163
00:14:22,090 --> 00:14:24,720
It's one of the three devil artifacts.

164
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:30,130
They interact with the demon fetus, provide Devil Lord's power to it,

165
00:14:30,130 --> 00:14:33,850
and also guide those who are looking for it.

166
00:14:33,850 --> 00:14:37,480
<i>The demon fetus. The Devil Lord's power.</i>

167
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:54,510
<i>[Soul-Gathering Spell]</i>

168
00:14:54,510 --> 00:14:57,000
<i>The Soul-Gathering Spell.</i>

169
00:14:57,930 --> 00:15:00,530
<i>No wonder Pang Yizhi wouldn't tell me.</i>

170
00:15:00,530 --> 00:15:03,430
<i>It's actually a forbidden devil spell.</i>

171
00:15:03,430 --> 00:15:05,960
<i>But I found it anyway.</i>

172
00:15:14,100 --> 00:15:16,530
<i>Now my progress on the Heartless Path</i>

173
00:15:16,530 --> 00:15:19,880
<i>is slower than the rate of my power's disappearance.</i>

174
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:24,300
<i>Besides, the Heartless Path isn't something that can be achieved shortly.</i>

175
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:28,820
<i>It seems like sealing the evil bone with my body won't be effective for too long.</i>

176
00:15:30,510 --> 00:15:35,110
<i>Maybe I can find other methods in the Guide to Devils.</i>

177
00:15:37,480 --> 00:15:43,820
♫ <i>Everything streamed by, sometimes well, other times wasted</i> ♫

178
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:51,540
♫ <i>Roads are longer than time, nobody to share my thoughts</i> ♫

179
00:15:51,540 --> 00:15:55,780
♫ <i>Bells ringing at sunset, I don't know what to write</i> ♫

180
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:59,520
♫ <i>I only dare to ask about how the spring breeze is</i> ♫

181
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:06,440
<i>[Soul-Gathering Spell]
Now, I've memorized the ways to launch the array.</i>

182
00:16:08,860 --> 00:16:12,460
♫ <i>Children spoke freely, sitting, embracing, and looking at the Milky Way</i> ♫

183
00:16:12,460 --> 00:16:13,963
<i>Wait.</i>

184
00:16:13,963 --> 00:16:17,100
<i>I didn't memorize the method of replacement that requires no soul.</i>

185
00:16:17,100 --> 00:16:22,960
♫ <i>Although green grass flourished and withered, the faces of the deceased are near in my memory</i> ♫

186
00:16:22,960 --> 00:16:27,200
♫ <i>The sound of fallen trees, I saw Gods when closing my eyes</i> ♫

187
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:30,300
♫ <i>Your joy, sorrow, and hatred were all illuminated</i> ♫

188
00:16:34,060 --> 00:16:37,720
♫ <i>Peach blossoms are blowing down, spring and autumn are blowing down</i> ♫

189
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:41,380
♫ <i>I understood the most was the moment in the dream</i> ♫

190
00:16:41,380 --> 00:16:45,620
♫ <i>Living long to wander, to awaken, repeat, to sojourn</i> ♫

191
00:16:45,620 --> 00:16:48,860
♫ <i>Living separately from the beginning to the end of the year</i> ♫

192
00:16:48,860 --> 00:16:52,980
♫ <i>So what about everywhere in the world, what about springtime</i> ♫

193
00:16:52,980 --> 00:16:56,100
♫ <i>I cannot ask for any of them </i> ♫

194
00:16:56,100 --> 00:17:00,420
♫ <i>"Fortunately" is nothing but all ordinary human affairs</i> ♫

195
00:17:00,420 --> 00:17:04,580
♫ <i>Compose an ordinary song</i> ♫

196
00:17:12,780 --> 00:17:16,110
<i>I've found the residence of the female immortal you told me to find.</i>

197
00:17:16,110 --> 00:17:19,510
<i>It's by the Heaven Lake of the Hengyang Sect.</i>

198
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:30,410
<i>[Demon Fetus]</i>

199
00:17:30,410 --> 00:17:34,490
<i>The origin of the Devil Lord is called the Demon Fetus.</i>

200
00:17:34,490 --> 00:17:38,700
<i>If the evil bone dwells in a body, it can turn into a new devil after accumulating sins.</i>

201
00:17:38,700 --> 00:17:43,730
<i>When it interacts with the devil artifacts, it'll obtain the Devil Lord's power.</i>

202
00:17:43,730 --> 00:17:49,040
<i>When it's born, its time, location, and host can't be told.</i>

203
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:51,010
<i>It's difficult to locate.</i>

204
00:17:51,010 --> 00:17:55,650
<i>The bone will not perish if its origin is not eradicated.</i>

205
00:17:57,400 --> 00:18:02,100
<i>According to these books, Tantai Jin is the demon fetus.</i>

206
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:04,790
<i>But it only says what the demon fetus is.</i>

207
00:18:04,790 --> 00:18:07,890
<i>It didn't state how to destroy the evil bone.</i>

208
00:18:07,890 --> 00:18:12,090
<i>Although my pure-spirit body can suppress the evil bone</i>

209
00:18:12,090 --> 00:18:14,410
<i>and be free from its corruption for now, </i>

210
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:17,780
<i>my power is receding day by day.</i>

211
00:18:17,790 --> 00:18:20,840
<i>I don't know how long I can maintain the seal.</i>

212
00:18:24,970 --> 00:18:29,110
<i>Seems like I can only use the divine energy of Mount Changze</i>

213
00:18:29,110 --> 00:18:31,720
<i>plus the assistance of Chongyu's power for now.</i>

214
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:34,820
<i>I can't afford to let the evil bone get out of control.</i>

215
00:18:48,960 --> 00:18:53,410
<i>That female immortal returned to this house.</i>

216
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:04,780
<i>Sorry for the interruption. My apologies.</i>

217
00:19:40,160 --> 00:19:41,980
<i>[Guide to Devils]</i>

218
00:19:45,020 --> 00:19:47,060
<i>[Guide to Devils]</i>

219
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:54,030
<i>[Soul-Gathering Array]</i>

220
00:19:57,620 --> 00:20:00,030
<i>This array needs to be stimulated by the soul of the deceased.</i>

221
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:04,800
<i>If no soul is available, a drop of blood from a pure-spirit body</i>

222
00:20:04,800 --> 00:20:07,570
<i>can gather the required soul as well.</i>

223
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:12,180
Gather the soul.

224
00:20:12,180 --> 00:20:15,160
The blood from a pure-spirit body.

225
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:20,440
<i>She has a pure-spirit body. Master was extremely protective of her.</i>

226
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:30,510
<i>If I can obtain Lady of Spirituality's blood, I can retrieve Ye Xiwu's soul.</i>

227
00:20:31,210 --> 00:20:35,643
<i>Maybe she can be like Gongye Jiwu.</i>

228
00:20:45,030 --> 00:20:46,300
<i>This Heaven Lake…</i>

229
00:20:46,300 --> 00:20:49,850
<i>I'm homesick when I see a full moon.</i>

230
00:20:49,850 --> 00:20:51,820
<i>There's also a lake in the vicinity.</i>

231
00:20:51,820 --> 00:20:55,610
<i>When it's summer, the lake water is clear and cool.</i>

232
00:20:55,610 --> 00:20:58,170
<i>I'll just lie by the lake and gaze at the stars.</i>

233
00:20:58,170 --> 00:21:02,940
<i>In the grass, there are fireflies flying around.</i>

234
00:21:02,940 --> 00:21:06,140
♫ <i>Mortal desires are like gazing upon the sudden disappearance of the moon</i> ♫

235
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:09,780
<i>What's the name of that lake?</i>

236
00:21:09,780 --> 00:21:11,290
<i>Where is it?</i>

237
00:21:12,690 --> 00:21:14,510
<i>It's somewhere far away.</i>

238
00:21:14,510 --> 00:21:17,960
<i>I'll take you there when there's a chance.</i>

239
00:21:18,540 --> 00:21:21,670
<i>Now, I'm here.</i>

240
00:21:21,670 --> 00:21:23,940
<i>But you are gone.</i>

241
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:30,120
♫ <i>Realization is washing away our memories in turbid water and rain</i> ♫

242
00:21:30,120 --> 00:21:34,960
♫ <i>We'll never meet again</i> ♫

243
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:39,480
♫ <i>I've seen the flowers bloom from soft-spoken words</i> ♫

244
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:42,480
♫ <i>Teary-eyed till all that's left was nonsense</i> ♫

245
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:44,420
The sounds of the harp.

246
00:21:44,420 --> 00:21:47,540
♫ <i>Love intertwines around the fragile titled roof</i> ♫

247
00:21:47,540 --> 00:21:51,340
♫ <i>Embracing the endless lingering fear</i> ♫

248
00:21:51,340 --> 00:21:54,960
♫ <i>I've admired you through the myriad of years</i> ♫

249
00:21:54,960 --> 00:21:58,980
♫ <i>I believed I have been loved for a moment</i> ♫

250
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:02,750
<i>What was that just now? Was it the evil bone?</i>

251
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:07,750
♫ <i>And become devout like the flawless moonlight</i> ♫

252
00:22:07,750 --> 00:22:11,510
<i>I'd better go meditate in the Spirit Well.</i>

253
00:22:26,040 --> 00:22:29,640
♫ <i>I'd admire your arrival when you came covered in scars</i> ♫

254
00:22:29,640 --> 00:22:32,930
♫ <i>And willingness to live a life in peace</i> ♫

255
00:22:32,930 --> 00:22:37,480
<i>I knew it. How could it be her?</i>

256
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:45,760
♫ <i>And learned to love what you used to resent</i> ♫

257
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:04,240
The Bone-Refining Seal is the Devil Lord's heart.

258
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:09,650
It will definitely guide us to find His Lordship's demon fetus.

259
00:23:09,650 --> 00:23:15,780
I didn't expect that we'd come to beg this old geezer one day.

260
00:23:15,780 --> 00:23:20,970
Even after 10,000 years, His Lordship's seal is still intact.

261
00:23:21,620 --> 00:23:27,880
I'd feel so delighted every time I heard Dimian's cry of agony.

262
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:29,600
Rest assured.

263
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:33,400
His Lordship's seal can only be undone by the Bone-Refining Seal.

264
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:36,100
Dimian won't be able to escape.

265
00:23:50,550 --> 00:23:57,580
<i>You've never come in the past 10,000 years.</i>

266
00:23:57,580 --> 00:24:00,880
<i>What's your business here today?</i>

267
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:03,680
Let's cut to the chase.

268
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:07,300
Dimian, you and Chuhuang had been married for many years.

269
00:24:07,300 --> 00:24:11,560
Do you know how to remove a seal that's enhanced by the gods?

270
00:24:11,560 --> 00:24:18,240
<i>If you need my help, don't you think you should tell me the whole story first?</i>

271
00:24:19,850 --> 00:24:24,900
During the last 500 years, although we didn't find the demon fetus,

272
00:24:24,900 --> 00:24:31,580
we accidentally discovered that the Bone-Refining Seal was sealed in the Shangqing God Realm.

273
00:24:32,200 --> 00:24:35,590
But the Bone-Refining Seal is guarded by the gods' seals.

274
00:24:35,590 --> 00:24:38,310
We can't retrieve it so easily.

275
00:24:39,580 --> 00:24:43,450
<i>So, now you've found a way in.</i>

276
00:24:43,450 --> 00:24:49,260
<i>And then, you want me to tell you how to undo the seal so that you can retrieve the artifact.</i>

277
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:04,050
<i>Take it.</i>

278
00:25:04,050 --> 00:25:11,550
<i>As long as you shoot the mantra into the seal, you should be able to remove the seal with your demonic power.</i>

279
00:25:11,550 --> 00:25:14,530
Lord of Monsters, you're surprisingly cooperative.

280
00:25:14,530 --> 00:25:18,010
<i>We'll thank you after we retrieve the artifact.</i>

281
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:28,440
<i>Finally, someone is looking for the Bone-Refining Seal for me.</i>

282
00:25:28,440 --> 00:25:32,100
<i>As long as they shoot the mantra in the seal, </i>

283
00:25:32,100 --> 00:25:37,730
<i>I will no longer need to stay in this hellhole.</i>

284
00:25:47,590 --> 00:25:50,660
One heavenly soldier. Skip.

285
00:25:50,660 --> 00:25:51,790
I'll take it if you don't.

286
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,660
One drought demon Siying.

287
00:25:53,660 --> 00:25:55,650
What game are you playing?

288
00:25:55,650 --> 00:25:58,310
This is called Devil VS God. It's super fun.

289
00:25:58,310 --> 00:26:01,240
It's said to be invented by Immortal Buxu.

290
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:02,510
It's popular around the four continents.

291
00:26:02,510 --> 00:26:05,060
Our Xiaoyao Sect is so proud of it.

292
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:07,440
- Junior Sect Brother, your card is the evil bone.
- Shuffle the cards.

293
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:09,350
Try it. You'll definitely love it.

294
00:26:09,350 --> 00:26:12,830
But it may backfire if paired with other identity cards.

295
00:26:12,830 --> 00:26:17,260
It'll be stronger if paired with the demon fetus because it will summon the ultimate Devil Lord.

296
00:26:17,260 --> 00:26:21,500
At this moment, if there are no identity cards of gods on the table, the Devil Lord will win.

297
00:26:21,500 --> 00:26:23,800
The ultimate Devil Lord?

298
00:26:23,800 --> 00:26:28,430
Yes. When the demon fetus and the evil bone are played together, the ultimate Devil Lord will resurrect.

299
00:26:28,430 --> 00:26:33,310
By then, the Devil Lord will possess devil artifacts like the God-Slaying Crossbow.

300
00:26:33,310 --> 00:26:37,640
If there's still no god showing up, the Devil Lord will be able to activate the ultimate weapon,

301
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:39,550
the All-in-Distress Path.

302
00:26:40,200 --> 00:26:45,230
But the Chronicles of Four Continents stated the Devil Lord was killed 10,000 years ago.

303
00:26:45,230 --> 00:26:47,070
The Devil Lord is born out of sins.

304
00:26:47,070 --> 00:26:51,100
As long as there's pain in the mortal world, the Devil Lord will be born one generation after another.

305
00:26:51,100 --> 00:26:54,710
When the demon fetus reappears, and the devil artifacts find their owner, the Devil Lord will be resurrected.

306
00:26:54,710 --> 00:26:59,753
The three realms will face destruction by then.

307
00:27:00,930 --> 00:27:07,520
Yeah. I heard that Yunchang Sect was wiped out by Siying and Jingmie, who were surviving members of the Devil Lord's reign.

308
00:27:07,520 --> 00:27:12,570
I heard the Yiyue Tribe, who made a pact with the Devil Lord to birth the demon fetus, lost the fetus.

309
00:27:12,570 --> 00:27:15,210
That's why they wreaked havoc.

310
00:27:15,210 --> 00:27:18,220
They're trying to find the fetus through the guidance of the devil artifacts.

311
00:27:18,220 --> 00:27:21,170
Then what do the artifacts have to do with Yunchang Sect?

312
00:27:21,170 --> 00:27:23,490
I have no idea.

313
00:27:23,890 --> 00:27:28,410
Anyway, the demon fetus is the origin of all evil. It's safe to say that.

314
00:27:28,410 --> 00:27:33,710
So they've been searching for it for 500 years. But they found nothing even until now?

315
00:27:33,710 --> 00:27:39,060
If the demon fetus refuses to show up, the Devil Lord won't be resurrected. Right?

316
00:27:39,060 --> 00:27:40,300
It's not as easy as that.

317
00:27:40,300 --> 00:27:43,170
Although the fetus's will may not be controlled by the Devil Lord,

318
00:27:43,170 --> 00:27:46,730
what the evil bone and devil artifacts carry is the Devil Lord's will.

319
00:27:46,730 --> 00:27:50,960
It's predestined. How can it be altered so easily?

320
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:54,993
If the demon fetus does show up, what will happen?

321
00:27:54,993 --> 00:27:58,550
If the fetus shows up now, the devils will surely go all out

322
00:27:58,550 --> 00:28:02,550
and do anything to awaken the fetus in order to revive the Devil Lord.

323
00:28:02,550 --> 00:28:04,590
Now, there's no god in this world.

324
00:28:04,590 --> 00:28:06,310
If they managed to revive the Devil Lord,

325
00:28:06,310 --> 00:28:12,190
even if the immortal sects try their best, I'm afraid we won't be able to stop his resurrection.

326
00:28:12,190 --> 00:28:15,540
The three realms' doom will be inevitable.

327
00:28:15,540 --> 00:28:17,030
That is so terrifying.

328
00:28:17,030 --> 00:28:20,390
Then we should go find the demon fetus and kill him before the devils find him!

329
00:28:20,390 --> 00:28:21,200
- Yeah!
- That's right!

330
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:23,400
What are you doing?

331
00:28:23,970 --> 00:28:25,550
- Master is here!
- Master.

332
00:28:25,550 --> 00:28:26,510
Slacking off again, huh?

333
00:28:26,510 --> 00:28:28,310
- Come on.
- Put them away.

334
00:28:28,310 --> 00:28:30,413
Come on. Hurry.

335
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,893
Master.

336
00:28:37,100 --> 00:28:38,533
Not bad.

337
00:28:38,533 --> 00:28:43,080
Despite training hard for the competition, you still remember to treat your master.

338
00:28:44,050 --> 00:28:46,200
Not bad at all.

339
00:28:48,730 --> 00:28:50,590
Sect Leader Cen is about to return from his traveling.

340
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:53,240
Please go welcome him at the hall, Junior Sect Leader.

341
00:29:10,510 --> 00:29:13,460
<i>Welcome back, Sect Leader.</i>

342
00:29:13,460 --> 00:29:15,780
Welcome back, Father.

343
00:29:24,110 --> 00:29:31,700
Mi'er, this Eight Direction Wind-Harnessing Fann is forged with rare spiritual gems from the four continents.

344
00:29:31,700 --> 00:29:33,970
It's perfect for you.

345
00:29:34,610 --> 00:29:37,210
- Take it.
- Thank you, Father.

346
00:29:37,210 --> 00:29:39,930
The Immortal Sect Competition is soon.

347
00:29:39,930 --> 00:29:44,110
I hope that you will train harder, kill more demons and devils,

348
00:29:44,110 --> 00:29:48,510
and preserve Chixiao Sect's good reputation.

349
00:29:48,510 --> 00:29:51,380
Yes. I shall not fail your expectation.

350
00:29:51,380 --> 00:29:54,750
Sect Leader, here's a letter from the leader of the Hengyang Sect.

351
00:29:58,800 --> 00:30:01,800
<i>[Recently, you found out that the devils, Siying and Jingmie were planning to break into Shangqing Realm.]</i>

352
00:30:01,800 --> 00:30:04,840
<i>[You have always been keen on eliminating devils. Let's take this chance to unite all sects]</i>

353
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:07,840
<i>[and defeat the two demons in one go. Time is of the essence. Please come soon for a discussion.]</i>

354
00:30:12,310 --> 00:30:18,010
The destruction of Yunchang Sect is a warning for all immortal sects.

355
00:30:18,010 --> 00:30:23,350
We must unite even more firmly and give the demon realm no chance.

356
00:30:23,350 --> 00:30:26,620
Nothing is more dangerous than underestimating our enemies.

357
00:30:26,620 --> 00:30:32,470
As per the current intel, the two devils are eager to enter Shangqing Realm.

358
00:30:32,470 --> 00:30:34,790
They must be after something.

359
00:30:34,790 --> 00:30:36,300
I think this intel is reliable.

360
00:30:36,300 --> 00:30:38,620
Last month, when I was assigning shift guards to keep guard

361
00:30:38,620 --> 00:30:40,780
over the entrance of Shangqing Realm, we suffered from a sneak attack.

362
00:30:40,780 --> 00:30:43,220
An elder even got severely injured.

363
00:30:43,220 --> 00:30:45,140
Thankfully, there was a barrier at the entrance.

364
00:30:45,140 --> 00:30:46,690
It didn't escalate to something bigger.

365
00:30:46,690 --> 00:30:47,970
That really happened?

366
00:30:47,970 --> 00:30:51,110
Back then, I thought Penglai Island offended somebody.

367
00:30:51,110 --> 00:30:54,900
I didn't expect that it was related to the two devils from Barren Abyss.

368
00:30:54,900 --> 00:30:56,820
The Immortal Sect Competition is imminent.

369
00:30:56,820 --> 00:31:03,520
For this event, we must select young blood to fight against the Devil Lord.

370
00:31:03,520 --> 00:31:09,400
Why don't we just let them come to this event and capture them in one fell swoop?

371
00:31:12,970 --> 00:31:17,930
According to Immortal Zhaoyou, since those two want to go to Shangqing God Realm

372
00:31:17,930 --> 00:31:22,510
let's host the competition right there.

373
00:31:22,510 --> 00:31:28,270
If they want to get something, we must deny all access to Shangqing God Realm.

374
00:31:28,270 --> 00:31:30,580
How could we host the competition there?

375
00:31:30,580 --> 00:31:35,960
Aren't we just inviting the wolf into the house and letting them have their way for nothing?

376
00:31:35,960 --> 00:31:39,720
Everyone, if we set a trap for them,

377
00:31:39,720 --> 00:31:44,720
we aren't inviting the wolf in but rather drawing the snake out.

378
00:31:46,380 --> 00:31:48,550
Well done.

379
00:31:48,550 --> 00:31:51,400
He has some skill.

380
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:53,540
What a poor pack of fervent champions of saviourhood!

381
00:31:53,540 --> 00:31:55,240
Their attempt to trick us won't work so easily.

382
00:31:55,240 --> 00:32:01,680
In that case, why not just do as they wish to live up to such a grand design?

383
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:05,260
All we want is the Bone-Refining Seal.

384
00:32:05,260 --> 00:32:07,850
There's no need to engage them in a conflict.

385
00:32:08,730 --> 00:32:14,150
I heard of a minor immortal sect at the North Sea called the Zixiu Isles.

386
00:32:14,150 --> 00:32:18,810
Perhaps we can pretend to be their sect members.

387
00:32:34,210 --> 00:32:36,620
Junior Brother, this is an old tradition.

388
00:32:36,620 --> 00:32:40,060
Every time we come to the Hengyang Sect, we're always served the roast chicken of Mount Changze,

389
00:32:40,060 --> 00:32:43,730
which has accumulated plenty of spiritual energy here and serves as a great source of nourishment.

390
00:32:43,730 --> 00:32:51,130
Following the direction upwards leads to the deities' former residence, the Shangqing God Realm.

391
00:32:51,130 --> 00:32:53,450
The Shangqing God Realm?

392
00:32:58,790 --> 00:33:02,010
<i>From this day forward, the Yuqing Palace will be closed.</i>

393
00:33:02,010 --> 00:33:06,410
<i>And the Shangqing Realm will house no god anymore.</i>

394
00:33:06,410 --> 00:33:10,313
<i>So all of you may go on your separate ways.</i>

395
00:33:11,270 --> 00:33:16,320
<i>Since God of War Mingye's departure, the Shangqing God Realm has been closed.</i>

396
00:33:17,250 --> 00:33:19,340
Junior Brother, you know it too?

397
00:33:19,340 --> 00:33:25,491
Our immortal sects were established according to the will of the gods to take over as champions of justice in the world.

398
00:33:25,491 --> 00:33:28,370
However, it's a hard job.

399
00:33:28,370 --> 00:33:30,270
Junior Brother, don't be so pessimistic.

400
00:33:30,270 --> 00:33:34,250
Once the competition is held, we can check it out.

401
00:33:34,250 --> 00:33:36,960
So will the competition be held in the Shangqing Realm?

402
00:33:36,960 --> 00:33:39,311
Exactly. The Heaven Gate of Triones is the entrance.

403
00:33:39,311 --> 00:33:42,310
The Heaven Gate of Triones could be found because of the war between the gods and the devils.

404
00:33:42,310 --> 00:33:46,730
The ancient Devil Lord broke the Heaven Pillar, which dipped and slit the Dome of Heaven.

405
00:33:46,730 --> 00:33:49,220
But it's usually invisible.

406
00:33:49,220 --> 00:33:53,250
Only by the joint effort of all the sect leaders can it be opened.

407
00:33:53,250 --> 00:33:57,110
By convention, all the immortal sects take turns hosting the competition.

408
00:33:57,110 --> 00:33:59,870
This year, it's the Chixiao Sect's turn.

409
00:33:59,870 --> 00:34:01,880
Sect Leader Cen is simply a miser.

410
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:05,130
He asked us to do the cleaning of the Shangqing God Realm.

411
00:34:05,130 --> 00:34:06,350
Clean what?

412
00:34:06,350 --> 00:34:12,420
Over the past 10,000 years, the departure of gods has left the Shangqing God Realm deserted,

413
00:34:12,420 --> 00:34:15,710
which became the habitat for some spirits and demons.

414
00:34:15,710 --> 00:34:22,560
This year, we are holding the competition in order to work together to clear the God Realm of evil spirits.

415
00:34:22,560 --> 00:34:25,880
And... the Lady of Spirituality is said to attend.

416
00:34:25,880 --> 00:34:28,110
She has got a reputation among the immortals.

417
00:34:28,110 --> 00:34:32,630
I am sure many want to meet her.

418
00:34:32,630 --> 00:34:35,170
<i>Li Susu will show up, too?</i>

419
00:34:35,170 --> 00:34:38,860
<i>It's a good chance to ask her for a drop of her blood.</i>

420
00:34:38,860 --> 00:34:43,760
Little Martial Aunt, no matter where I am, people always talk about you.

421
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:48,470
Even some guys have asserted that it doesn't matter if they win the competition.

422
00:34:48,470 --> 00:34:52,380
What matters most is to win the gorgeous lady's heart.

423
00:34:53,550 --> 00:34:55,770
Just ignore them.

424
00:34:55,770 --> 00:35:00,590
No. Those libertines should avoid me at all costs.

425
00:35:00,590 --> 00:35:05,360
If not, I'll definitely beat them up.

426
00:35:06,510 --> 00:35:08,180
You're so fierce.

427
00:35:08,180 --> 00:35:12,110
Those young disciples will definitely hide from you when they see you tomorrow.

428
00:35:12,110 --> 00:35:14,310
You won't be able to beat them up.

429
00:35:18,360 --> 00:35:21,993
Little Martial Aunt, I have an idea.

430
00:35:29,190 --> 00:35:30,790
Hold it.

431
00:35:31,423 --> 00:35:33,510
What are you doing?

432
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:36,113
It's done.

433
00:35:40,710 --> 00:35:42,230
You little sprite.

434
00:35:42,230 --> 00:35:46,440
Little Martial Aunt, you can be at ease tomorrow.

435
00:35:46,440 --> 00:35:49,760
Just leave the rest to me.

436
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:51,450
What are you thinking this time?

437
00:35:51,450 --> 00:35:59,240
I have an enchanted silk veil, which can obscure the face of the person who wears it.

438
00:35:59,240 --> 00:36:01,560
Then I'll disguise myself as you

439
00:36:01,560 --> 00:36:07,070
and teach those libertines a lesson.

440
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:13,320
I think you're just trying to play a trick on them to have fun.

441
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:16,410
Fine. You need to have a bottom line.

442
00:36:16,410 --> 00:36:18,460
Don't go overboard.

443
00:36:18,460 --> 00:36:21,960
Okay. I promise I won't. Rest assured, Little Martial Aunt.

444
00:36:28,660 --> 00:36:30,740
All the immortal sects are here.

445
00:36:30,740 --> 00:36:32,790
We should depart, too.

446
00:36:40,860 --> 00:36:43,240
<i>[Qianji School]</i>

447
00:36:43,240 --> 00:36:45,380
<i>[Xionggui Pavilion]</i>

448
00:36:50,060 --> 00:36:51,740
<i>[Hongluan Palace]</i>

449
00:36:51,740 --> 00:36:53,400
<i>[Yaowang Valley]</i>

450
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:55,300
<i>[Shanhai Alliance]</i>

451
00:37:02,380 --> 00:37:03,940
<i>[Penglai Island]</i>

452
00:37:03,940 --> 00:37:06,100
<i>[Xiaoyao Sect]</i>

453
00:37:06,100 --> 00:37:08,760
<i>[The Chixiao Sect]</i>

454
00:37:12,700 --> 00:37:16,200
<i>[Unification of Heaven and Earth]</i>

455
00:37:22,530 --> 00:37:24,880
All the immortal sects are here.

456
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:27,440
Who are they?

457
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:30,220
Hi. We are from the Shanhai Alliance.

458
00:37:30,220 --> 00:37:33,460
May I know which sect you're from?

459
00:37:36,550 --> 00:37:40,090
We are disciples of Immortal Beichen from the Zixiu Isles.

460
00:37:40,090 --> 00:37:41,440
The Zixiu Isles?

461
00:37:41,440 --> 00:37:43,960
It's a minor immortal sect at the North Sea.

462
00:37:43,960 --> 00:37:45,410
Nice to meet you.

463
00:37:45,410 --> 00:37:47,360
Let's go. Let's go.

464
00:37:51,690 --> 00:37:54,050
What a huge crowd!

465
00:37:56,960 --> 00:37:58,670
Look, it's the Hengyang Sect.

466
00:37:58,670 --> 00:38:01,020
Seems like it's almost time to begin.

467
00:38:04,070 --> 00:38:06,250
Lady of Spirituality!

468
00:38:06,250 --> 00:38:09,700
She's gorgeous! She's beautiful!

469
00:38:09,700 --> 00:38:11,360
That's the Lady of Spirituality?

470
00:38:11,360 --> 00:38:13,360
She's not as attractive as we've heard.

471
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:15,110
She wears a magic veil.

472
00:38:15,110 --> 00:38:16,960
You can't see behind it.

473
00:38:16,960 --> 00:38:20,840
- I presume only a Heaven-fated one can know
what she really looks like.
<i>- That's Li Susu?</i>

474
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:27,220
<i>I just need to ask her for a drop of her blood, and Ye Xiwu will…</i>

475
00:38:28,440 --> 00:38:30,030
Lady of Spirituality.

476
00:38:30,030 --> 00:38:32,360
Look. That's Cen Mi.

477
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:39,510
By the authority of his father, the sect leader of one of the Three Sects, he is arrogant, avaricious, and lascivious.

478
00:38:39,510 --> 00:38:46,490
Ladies and gentlemen, welcome to the Competition of Immortal Sects.

479
00:38:49,820 --> 00:38:54,670
The criterion is the same as that of the previous.

480
00:38:54,670 --> 00:39:01,900
That is, how many demons you catch and how long it takes.

481
00:39:01,900 --> 00:39:05,280
Each competitor will receive an empty Demon-Confining Sachet.

482
00:39:05,280 --> 00:39:08,380
During the Competition, whenever

483
00:39:08,380 --> 00:39:13,130
you feel you've had enough, you may leave the venue.

484
00:39:13,130 --> 00:39:18,430
Finally, depending on how long you spend and how much your sachets weigh,

485
00:39:18,430 --> 00:39:23,230
your rank will be determined.

486
00:39:24,410 --> 00:39:26,900
You can find partners.

487
00:39:26,900 --> 00:39:30,200
But each group may consist of no more than three members.

488
00:39:43,670 --> 00:39:45,360
It's almost time to begin.

489
00:39:45,360 --> 00:39:49,993
Everyone, get ready to depart.

490
00:40:51,190 --> 00:40:55,410
<i>Shangqing God Realm has changed so much.</i>

491
00:40:55,920 --> 00:40:59,770
<i>My top priority now is to find the pure-spirit body.</i>

492
00:40:59,770 --> 00:41:04,633
My brothers, it's a rare chance to get access to this realm.

493
00:41:04,633 --> 00:41:06,100
I have no intention of winning the competition.

494
00:41:06,100 --> 00:41:09,320
I just want to explore and widen my horizon.

495
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:12,680
I won't accompany you guys.

496
00:41:12,680 --> 00:41:14,560
Please excuse me.

497
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:16,970
Junior Brother!

498
00:41:16,970 --> 00:41:17,820
Lady of Spirituality.

499
00:41:17,820 --> 00:41:18,960
- Lady of Spirituality.
- Miss Susu.

500
00:41:18,960 --> 00:41:20,630
I'm Liu Jianghai, the premier swordsman of Shanhai Alliance.

501
00:41:20,630 --> 00:41:22,670
Have you heard of the title of my sword? It's Rivers-in-Reverse.

502
00:41:22,670 --> 00:41:23,840
I learned that you've just finished your secluded cultivation.

503
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:25,950
So I brought my sect's prized treasures especially for you to appreciate.

504
00:41:25,950 --> 00:41:26,880
Could you please do me an honor?

505
00:41:26,880 --> 00:41:30,160
Lady of Spirituality, would you mind being my partner?

506
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:33,130
Gosh! What's that?

507
00:41:35,670 --> 00:41:36,410
Lady of Spirituality?

508
00:41:36,410 --> 00:41:38,343
Miss Susu?

509
00:41:39,920 --> 00:41:41,230
Little Crescent has told me about your plan.

510
00:41:41,230 --> 00:41:45,800
This trick will cause you two to be blacklisted.

511
00:41:45,800 --> 00:41:47,441
It doesn't matter. I don't like being bothered.

512
00:41:47,441 --> 00:41:51,180
She likes playing pranks. We're killing two birds with one stone.

513
00:41:51,180 --> 00:41:54,320
If it makes you uncomfortable, I can get rid of the disguise.

514
00:42:00,180 --> 00:42:01,913
Susu,

515
00:42:01,913 --> 00:42:05,160
I cannot be your partner this year.

516
00:42:05,160 --> 00:42:07,440
You just got out of your meditative retreat, don't push yourself too much.

517
00:42:07,440 --> 00:42:10,371
Don't worry. I'll just take a stroll to clear my mind.

518
00:42:11,050 --> 00:42:13,780
<i>My immortal friends, </i>

519
00:42:13,780 --> 00:42:18,000
<i>the barriers of all regions will soon be opened.</i>

520
00:42:18,000 --> 00:42:21,570
<i>Let's make it a fair competition</i>

521
00:42:21,570 --> 00:42:26,790
<i>and rid Shangqing God Realm of demons.</i>

522
00:42:26,790 --> 00:42:31,513
<i>Now, the competition officially begins.</i>

523
00:42:44,760 --> 00:42:46,840
We've put so much effort into this.

524
00:42:46,840 --> 00:42:50,090
Let's hope the two demons will take the bait.

525
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:54,210
<i>Great. A plan to lure the snake out.</i>

526
00:42:54,210 --> 00:42:57,760
<i>I wonder what Sect Leader Qu has in mind?</i>

527
00:42:57,760 --> 00:43:01,340
<i>Since the first competition, all immortal sect members know</i>

528
00:43:01,340 --> 00:43:03,460
<i>that as long as you chant the mantra during the event,</i>

529
00:43:03,460 --> 00:43:06,360
<i>you'll be teleported back to the Hengyang Sect.</i>

530
00:43:06,360 --> 00:43:08,610
<i>As long as the two devils show up in front of our disciples,</i>

531
00:43:08,610 --> 00:43:13,040
<i>we'll be able to lock onto the two devils based on the position of our disciples.</i>

532
00:43:13,040 --> 00:43:16,910
<i>By then, we'll set up the barrier, and we shall eliminate them personally.</i>

533
00:43:19,030 --> 00:43:22,363
Siying, demonic energy is abundant here.

534
00:43:22,363 --> 00:43:26,480
The Bone-Refining Seal must be here.

535
00:43:27,550 --> 00:43:29,340
Nian Baiyu,

536
00:43:30,550 --> 00:43:31,600
search over there.

537
00:43:31,600 --> 00:43:34,810
Report to us if you find anything.

538
00:43:34,810 --> 00:43:36,533
Yes.

539
00:43:41,480 --> 00:43:42,700
What?

540
00:43:42,700 --> 00:43:46,860
You still don't trust him even whenhe had followed us for 500 years?

541
00:43:46,860 --> 00:43:48,630
What do you know?

542
00:43:48,630 --> 00:43:51,330
You can't read their minds.

543
00:43:55,450 --> 00:43:57,183
Let's go.

544
00:44:24,780 --> 00:44:26,413
You!

545
00:44:31,660 --> 00:44:33,293
Harder.

546
00:44:33,293 --> 00:44:35,220
Greetings, Junior Sect Leader.

547
00:44:43,490 --> 00:44:48,230
As long as you do a good job, Chixiao Sect will reward you generously.

548
00:44:49,860 --> 00:44:52,280
Thank you, Junior Sect Leader.

549
00:44:52,280 --> 00:44:54,133
Junior Sect Leader!

550
00:44:57,340 --> 00:44:59,890
We've found the whereabouts of the Lady of Spirituality.

551
00:45:03,360 --> 00:45:05,530
<i>Shangqing Realm is a vast place.</i>

552
00:45:05,530 --> 00:45:08,461
<i>Even if I had entered Mingye's Enlightened Life before,</i>

553
00:45:08,461 --> 00:45:11,070
<i>looking for Li Susu is still like</i>

554
00:45:11,070 --> 00:45:13,720
<i>dredging for a needle in the sea.</i>

555
00:45:16,090 --> 00:45:20,523
<i>Those are disciples of Chixiao Sect.</i>

556
00:45:48,130 --> 00:45:50,080
It's you.

557
00:45:50,630 --> 00:45:53,580
Junior Chief Cen, I've never offended you before.

558
00:45:53,580 --> 00:45:55,640
Why did you snatch my things?

559
00:45:56,630 --> 00:45:57,820
What are you looking at?

560
00:45:57,820 --> 00:46:01,450
If you may be so kind, Lady Susu,

561
00:46:01,450 --> 00:46:05,790
why don't you let me see your face?

562
00:46:08,300 --> 00:46:12,300
Not only will I return the Demon-Confining Sachet to you,

563
00:46:12,300 --> 00:46:18,640
but I'm also willing to watch the ruins of Shangqing with you.

564
00:46:21,150 --> 00:46:26,360
How can Sect Leader Cen have such a shameless son like you?

565
00:46:26,360 --> 00:46:28,330
You scoundrel!

566
00:46:32,570 --> 00:46:34,103
Go!

567
00:46:55,030 --> 00:46:56,070
Let go of me!

568
00:46:56,070 --> 00:46:57,903
Let go of me!

569
00:47:00,930 --> 00:47:05,070
If you prefer not to take your veil off yourself,

570
00:47:07,260 --> 00:47:11,440
allow me to do it for you.

571
00:47:14,260 --> 00:47:17,100
You're as pretty as expected!

572
00:47:17,100 --> 00:47:20,660
Lady Susu, I've been admiring you for so long.

573
00:47:20,660 --> 00:47:24,280
Please accept my feelings today.

574
00:47:24,280 --> 00:47:26,130
Don't touch me.

575
00:47:26,760 --> 00:47:29,000
If you do it again, I'll shout for help.

576
00:47:29,000 --> 00:47:31,440
This is just a matter between lovers. No need to shout.

577
00:47:31,440 --> 00:47:32,820
You rogue!

578
00:47:32,820 --> 00:47:35,070
Who said we are lovers?

579
00:47:35,070 --> 00:47:37,210
In your dreams!

580
00:47:51,480 --> 00:47:54,413
Who's there? Who dares to attack me?

581
00:47:54,413 --> 00:47:56,093
Come out!

582
00:48:11,920 --> 00:48:13,320
Who are you?

583
00:48:13,320 --> 00:48:16,640
Cang Jiumin of the Xiaoyao Sect.

584
00:48:16,640 --> 00:48:18,460
This matter is between the Chixiao and Hengyang Sects.

585
00:48:18,460 --> 00:48:20,640
As a disciple of Xiaoyao Sect, this is none of your business. Stop interfering!

586
00:48:20,640 --> 00:48:22,690
But I've interfered already.

587
00:48:22,690 --> 00:48:26,440
If you disagree, why don't you use your sword to prove it?

588
00:48:37,630 --> 00:48:39,900
Cang Jiumin, I'm the son of a sect leader!

589
00:48:39,900 --> 00:48:41,880
Don't tell me you're going to kill me?

590
00:48:41,880 --> 00:48:42,510
I dare not.

591
00:48:42,510 --> 00:48:44,280
Then why don't you pull back your swords?

592
00:48:44,280 --> 00:48:45,913
However,

593
00:48:45,913 --> 00:48:48,960
this is a vast realm with many dangerous demonic spirits.

594
00:48:48,960 --> 00:48:54,690
It's common for one disciple or two to die in this place.

595
00:48:55,510 --> 00:48:58,600
Junior Brother Cang, let's talk this through.

596
00:48:58,600 --> 00:49:00,480
There's no need to fight each other.

597
00:49:00,500 --> 00:49:02,600
All right then. Apologize.

598
00:49:02,610 --> 00:49:05,660
Sorry! I shouldn't have attacked you just now.

599
00:49:05,660 --> 00:49:09,430
I mean, you should apologize to Miss Susu.

600
00:49:09,430 --> 00:49:12,580
Lady Susu, sorry for being a toad wanting swan meat.

601
00:49:12,580 --> 00:49:16,790
Please be magnanimous and tell Junior Brother Cang to spare me.

602
00:49:18,010 --> 00:49:18,960
Forget it.

603
00:49:18,960 --> 00:49:21,810
He's the son of Sect Leader Cen. We can't do anything against him.

604
00:49:21,810 --> 00:49:22,590
Please!

605
00:49:22,590 --> 00:49:23,840
Let me live.

606
00:49:23,840 --> 00:49:26,680
I'd like to give back your Demon-Confining Sachet, Lady Susu.

607
00:49:32,700 --> 00:49:34,533
Get lost!

608
00:49:42,400 --> 00:49:44,860
Miss Susu, look after your sachet.

609
00:49:44,860 --> 00:49:46,213
Thank you.

610
00:49:46,213 --> 00:49:49,010
You're Cang Jiumin.

611
00:49:49,010 --> 00:49:50,940
Thanks for helping me out.

612
00:49:50,940 --> 00:49:54,480
Earlier did you use the Xiaoyao Sword-play?

613
00:49:54,480 --> 00:49:56,130
It was my first time seeing it.

614
00:49:56,130 --> 00:49:58,400
May I know who your master is?

615
00:49:58,400 --> 00:50:00,290
Miss Susu, you don't need to be this courteous.

616
00:50:00,290 --> 00:50:02,580
It was nothing.

617
00:50:02,580 --> 00:50:05,963
I am the disciple of Immortal Zhaoyou.

618
00:50:05,963 --> 00:50:11,310
I heard from my master that Immortal Zhaoyou just took in a young disciple

619
00:50:11,310 --> 00:50:13,320
who had immense potential.

620
00:50:13,320 --> 00:50:15,940
It turns out you're the one.

621
00:50:27,340 --> 00:50:29,570
The demonic energy is getting denser.

622
00:50:29,570 --> 00:50:32,610
The thing we're looking for should be in that direction.

623
00:50:32,610 --> 00:50:34,180
We can't blow our covers.

624
00:50:34,180 --> 00:50:38,560
We can only walk in this vast Shangqing Realm.

625
00:50:38,560 --> 00:50:40,780
What a bummer.

626
00:50:41,300 --> 00:50:42,900
Shangqing Realm isn't our home ground.

627
00:50:42,900 --> 00:50:45,400
Let's try to avoid direct conflicts.

628
00:51:02,710 --> 00:51:06,160
<i>They dress like the disciples of Zixiu Isles.</i>

629
00:51:24,030 --> 00:51:26,630
Greetings, I'm Gongye Jiwu of the Hengyang Sect.

630
00:51:26,630 --> 00:51:28,190
I'm Xisheng from Penglai Island.

631
00:51:28,190 --> 00:51:30,890
My master is Leader Liuzhi. Nice to meet you.

632
00:51:30,890 --> 00:51:33,730
You're indeed gentle and cultured. I've been looking forward to meeting you.

633
00:51:36,360 --> 00:51:37,793
<i>Jiwu,</i>

634
00:51:37,793 --> 00:51:40,590
<i>this time, the Immortal Sect Competition is totally different.</i>

635
00:51:40,590 --> 00:51:43,590
<i>I have a more important task to entrust to you.</i>

636
00:51:43,590 --> 00:51:45,490
<i>After the beginning of the competition,</i>

637
00:51:45,490 --> 00:51:48,490
<i>you need to work with the disciples of Penglai Island and Xionggui Sect</i>

638
00:51:48,490 --> 00:51:52,190
<i>and search for those two devils in Shangqing God Realm.</i>

639
00:51:52,740 --> 00:51:56,720
<i>Once you find those two devils in Shangqing God Realm, make a report as soon as possible.</i>

640
00:51:56,720 --> 00:51:59,180
<i>Shangqing God Realm has the most pure energy in the world.</i>

641
00:51:59,180 --> 00:52:00,180
<i>It is harmful to demons and devils.</i>

642
00:52:00,180 --> 00:52:03,000
<i>And disciples of immortal sects can improve their skills better there.</i>

643
00:52:03,000 --> 00:52:06,860
<i>Once Siying and Jingmie come, we can use this opportunity</i>

644
00:52:06,860 --> 00:52:09,250
<i>to take them down.</i>

645
00:52:11,110 --> 00:52:12,740
The competition has been on for a while.

646
00:52:12,740 --> 00:52:14,960
The two of us have been doing our rounds.

647
00:52:14,960 --> 00:52:16,530
But we found nothing out of the ordinary.

648
00:52:16,530 --> 00:52:19,920
Could it be that no devils have snuck in at all?

649
00:52:28,380 --> 00:52:31,980
If they change their appearance and dress up as disciples,

650
00:52:31,980 --> 00:52:34,960
they will be difficult to spot.

651
00:52:38,400 --> 00:52:40,700
By the way, Cang Jiumin,

652
00:52:42,130 --> 00:52:45,490
have you ever seen me after you have settled down here?

653
00:52:45,490 --> 00:52:47,023
No, I haven't.

654
00:52:47,023 --> 00:52:49,400
I've only heard of you.

655
00:52:50,780 --> 00:52:54,290
<i>My plan of pretending to be Li Susu has created a mess.</i>

656
00:52:54,290 --> 00:52:57,600
<i>If I tell him the truth, will he get angry?</i>

657
00:52:57,600 --> 00:52:59,710
Cang Jiumin,

658
00:53:01,090 --> 00:53:02,723
I…

659
00:53:05,700 --> 00:53:08,130
What is that place?

660
00:53:09,500 --> 00:53:11,250
That's the Yuqing Palace.

661
00:53:11,250 --> 00:53:16,700
<i>It used to be where the gods' nuptials, funerals, and rituals took place 10,000 years ago.</i>

662
00:53:16,700 --> 00:53:19,180
<i>In the end, </i>

663
00:53:19,180 --> 00:53:21,330
<i>I still came back here.</i>

664
00:53:22,190 --> 00:53:26,110
<i>Tantai Jin, it's so hard...</i>

665
00:53:26,920 --> 00:53:29,020
<i>to erase you from my mind.</i>

666
00:53:30,180 --> 00:53:35,530
<i>Why is there always a trace of you no matter where I go?</i>

667
00:53:36,670 --> 00:53:44,303
<i>Mingye, I want to ask you one thing. Have you ever, even a little bit,</i>

668
00:53:46,550 --> 00:53:49,360
<i>for even one second,</i>

669
00:53:51,220 --> 00:53:53,450
<i>had any feelings for me?</i>

670
00:53:56,860 --> 00:53:58,793
<i>Mingye, </i>

671
00:53:58,793 --> 00:54:03,230
<i>in order to fight against the Devil Lord and safeguard the world, </i>

672
00:54:03,230 --> 00:54:05,740
<i>you gave up on Sang Jiu.</i>

673
00:54:05,740 --> 00:54:08,050
<i>How did you do that?</i>

674
00:54:11,630 --> 00:54:14,290
<i>Why am I always so indecisive?</i>

675
00:54:15,000 --> 00:54:18,150
<i>I am always immersed in my memories of 500 years ago.</i>

676
00:54:18,150 --> 00:54:20,130
<i>I can't help it.</i>

677
00:54:24,050 --> 00:54:28,383
<i>Mingye, you and Sang Jiu were separated.</i>

678
00:54:28,383 --> 00:54:31,360
<i>It's the same for Ye Xiwu and me.</i>

679
00:54:32,820 --> 00:54:34,653
Miss Li,

680
00:54:35,400 --> 00:54:40,940
can you do me a favor?

681
00:54:48,710 --> 00:54:54,670
It turns out that you want to take a drop of my pure-spirit body's blood

682
00:54:54,670 --> 00:54:58,290
to retrieve your wife's soul?

683
00:54:58,290 --> 00:55:03,390
- I thought…
- May I have a drop of it?

684
00:55:03,390 --> 00:55:06,200
I don't need a lot, only a drop of it.

685
00:55:06,200 --> 00:55:11,833
In exchange, I'll agree to whatever condition you bring up.

686
00:55:14,150 --> 00:55:19,320
Well… Cang Jiumin, I-I'm not a petty person.

687
00:55:19,320 --> 00:55:21,920
And I'd love to help you get your wife back.

688
00:55:21,920 --> 00:55:25,840
But I'm sorry I can't give you a pure-spirit body's blood.

689
00:55:26,660 --> 00:55:28,193
Why?

690
00:55:28,193 --> 00:55:30,683
Actually...

691
00:55:30,683 --> 00:55:34,110
<i>Actually, I lied to you. I'm not Li Susu.</i>

692
00:55:34,110 --> 00:55:37,720
<i>She's my martial aunt. My name is Yue Ya.</i>

693
00:55:37,720 --> 00:55:39,970
<i>So where is Li Susu?</i>

694
00:55:52,380 --> 00:55:54,930
<i>Why don't you try one?</i>

695
00:56:04,840 --> 00:56:08,450
The severed Red Immortal Fruit Tree

696
00:56:08,450 --> 00:56:12,810
was able to sprout after 10,000 years.

697
00:56:13,700 --> 00:56:17,010
Even a tree like you gets a second chance.

698
00:56:30,120 --> 00:56:32,690
<i>I must get more than you!</i>

699
00:56:34,490 --> 00:56:35,890
Senior Brother, aren't we waiting for Jiumin?

700
00:56:35,890 --> 00:56:37,550
